data.description:
Wonderfully made, wonderfully maintained 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home. Master and laundry are on the main. The full basement is unfinished but partially zoned control. 6 foot privacy fence with gated entry for the back yard. Lovely back deck for your summer time grilling. The back yard is very private! Back inside you will find a quaint kitchen with stunning granite counter tops open to the dining area then flowing directly in to the living room. Schedule your showing today!

Buyer/Buyers agent to verify all info. All info deemed reliable as retrieved from seller and CRS.
